{"tid":1442121,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"福建幫晒馬：人若犯我 我必自慰","createTime":"2019-08-10T23:33:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T02:39:34.000Z","uid":143472,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c1b7ea5ab0a00a7d1a0d65fa7b6533f846a559ca","tid":1442121,"uid":143472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T23:33:04.000Z","msg":"香港福建社團聯會昨在北角舉行「止暴制亂、反獨保家誓師大會」，聯會主席吳換炎致辭時擺明車馬指今日有示威者在維園集會，鄉親們要照顧好家庭、保護聯會會所及財產等，揚言「人不犯我，我不犯人；人若犯我，我必自衞」。<br />\n<br />\n吳換炎回應如何「自衞」時改稱不是要福建人出手，只是希望福建人守住聯會會所，聲稱「<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我哋自慰只會喺入面（室內）自慰，唔係喺出面自慰，就喺屋企自慰，唔會出門口自慰，放心啦！</span>」強調「唔會出嚟打人」，具體的「自衞」只是「飲茶、傾偈」，有需要時報警，又多次重申福建人「一定要冷靜、一定要克制」，他亦與上周一打人的福建幫白衫暴徒切割，聲稱對此毫不知情。"},{"pid":"a9152cd853d79a8c4eb272ac4fd68459443259d5","tid":1442121,"uid":140326,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T23:35:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今日北角空城計,等佢比錢請人黎無目標打，邊個吹雞去北角 一係鬼一係on9</span></span>"},{"pid":"698226d35b91171497dd732a44431fc432f9745f","tid":1442121,"uid":120715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T23:42:03.000Z","msg":"打俾入境處先<br />\n懷疑有非法入境者"},{"pid":"fb291d07eaa70f23727791ce58da9f650c3524f4","tid":1442121,"uid":143472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T23:59:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190811/20747033\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190811%2F20747033&d=haqyWHVU0l66G8glzozbUwjMvzJQG4GdM8cyRMJzdLg%3D&h=60d28b20\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190811%2F20747033&h=2a3759cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190811/20747033</a><br />\n<br />\n貼番條link"},{"pid":"0b1f99079eaa5f8822a85422f0e78bf06b31c680","tid":1442121,"uid":57723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9152cd853d79a8c4eb272ac4fd68459443259d5","tid":1442121,"uid":140326,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T23:35:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今日北角空城計,等佢比錢請人黎無目標打，邊個吹雞去北角 一係鬼一係on9</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T00:01:56.000Z","msg":"老毛: 敵進我退 敵駐我擾 敵疲我打 敵退我追"},{"pid":"0fdc716ef9e53cde589efaa301b22a6ab9888e63","tid":1442121,"uid":216789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T02:39:34.000Z","msg":"<strong>慎防黑惡勢力蔓延禍港，提防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團</strong><br />\n<br />\n鑒於近日有無辜香港市民慘遭黑勢力人仕襲擊，現懇切呼籲各香港市民不論男女，請慎防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團，保障自身安全，萬事小心，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">切忌助長黑惡勢力氣焰</span></strong>"}]}